This is a collab!

⏷ IN DEVELOPMENT ⏷

You play as the player in a platformer, but watch out - there's a twist! The game dev is still working on his game and he keeps adding new things! From falling blocks to appearing spikes, you've had enough! His game is still "in development" and you'll have to beat it!

Created by BagelBytes

» WASD, Mobile, or Arrow Keys to move.
» Avoid spikes and enemies!
» Don't let the game dev drop any blocks on you!
» Win the game!

❤️&⭐️ to bring the game dev's dream to life :)

